<li id="cite_note-2"><span class="mw-cite-backlink" id="mwBVo"><a href="#cite_ref-2" id="mwBVs"><span class="mw-linkback-text" id="mwBVw">â </span></a></span> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-2" class="mw-reference-text reference-text"><cite id="CITEREFKenneth_M._Stampp1980" class="citation book cs1">Kenneth M. Stampp (1980). <a href="https://books.google.com/books?id=J6I87GxnOBEC&amp;pg=PA85" class="external text external" id="mwBV4"><i id="mwBV8">The Imperiled Union:Essays on the Background of the Civil War</i></a>. Oxford University Press. p.<span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwBWA">&nbsp;</span>85. ISBN<span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwBWI">&nbsp;</span><bdi id="mwBWQ">9780199878529</bdi>.</cite></span></li>
