<li id="cite_note-77"><span class="mw-cite-backlink" id="mwByo"><a href="#cite_ref-77" id="mwBys"><span class="mw-linkback-text" id="mwByw">â </span></a></span> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-77" class="mw-reference-text reference-text">Harrison, "Lawfulness of the Reconstruction Amendments" (2001), pp. 394â397.</span></li>
<li id="cite_note-78"><span class="mw-cite-backlink" id="mwBy0"><a href="#cite_ref-78" id="mwBy4"><span class="mw-linkback-text" id="mwBy8">â </span></a></span> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-78" class="mw-reference-text reference-text"><cite id="CITEREFEric_L._McKitrick1960" class="citation book cs1">Eric L. McKitrick (1960). <a href="https://books.google.com/books?id=MqL8lmT74HEC&amp;pg=PA178" class="external text external" id="mwBzE"><i id="mwBzI">Andrew Johnson and Reconstruction</i></a>. U. Chicago Press. p.<span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwBzM">&nbsp;</span>178. ISBN<span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwBzU">&nbsp;</span><bdi id="mwBzc">9780195057072</bdi>.</cite><span id="mwBzk"> </span><span class="cs1-hidden-error citation-comment" id="mwBzo"><code class="cs1-code" id="mwBzs">{{cite book}}</code>: </span><span class="cs1-hidden-error citation-comment" id="mwBz0">ISBN / Date incompatibility (help)</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-79"><span class="mw-cite-backlink" id="mwB0A"><a href="#cite_ref-79" id="mwB0E"><span class="mw-linkback-text" id="mwB0I">â </span></a></span> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-79" class="mw-reference-text reference-text"><cite id="CITEREFClara_Mildred_Thompson1915" class="citation book cs1">Clara Mildred Thompson (1915). <a href="https://archive.org/details/bub_gb_i5shAQAAIAAJ" class="external text external" id="mwB0Q"><i id="mwB0U">Reconstruction in Georgia: economic, social, political, 1865â1872</i></a>. Columbia University Press. p.<span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwB0Y">&nbsp;</span><a href="https://archive.org/details/bub_gb_i5shAQAAIAAJ/page/n162" class="external text external" id="mwB0c">156</a>.</cite></span></li>
