<li id="cite_note-139"><span class="mw-cite-backlink" id="mwCQY"><a href="#cite_ref-139" id="mwCQc"><span class="mw-linkback-text" id="mwCQg">â </span></a></span> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-139" class="mw-reference-text reference-text"><cite id="CITEREFNilsen2018" class="citation news cs1">Nilsen, Ella (October 11, 2018). <a href="https://www.vox.com/2018/10/11/17964558/kanye-west-donald-trump-white-house-13th-amendment" class="external text external" id="mwCQo">"Kanye West's meeting with President Trump turned into an extended rant on mental health and the 13th Amendment"</a>. <i id="mwCQs">Vox</i>. <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20200609020401/https://www.vox.com/2018/10/11/17964558/kanye-west-donald-trump-white-house-13th-amendment" class="external text external" id="mwCQ0">Archived</a> from the original on June 9, 2020<span class="reference-accessdate" id="mwCQ4">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap" id="mwCQ8">October 27,</span> 2018</span>.</cite></span></li>
