<ul id="mwC1Y"><li id="mwC1c"><i id="mwC1g">Panel III: The Limits of Authority</i></li></ul>
<dl id="mwC1k"><dd id="mwC1o"><ul id="mwC1s"><li id="mwC1w"><cite id="CITEREFGreene2012" class="citation journal cs1">Greene, Jamal (November 2012). <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20150107063310/http://columbialawreview.org/thirteenth-amendment-optimism" class="external text external">"Thirteenth Amendment optimism"</a>. <i>Columbia Law Review</i>. <b>112</b> (7). Columbia Law School: <span class="nowrap">1733â</span>1768. JSTOR<span typeof="mw:Entity">&nbsp;</span><a href="https://www.jstor.org/stable/41708163" class="external text external">41708163</a>. Archived from <a href="http://columbialawreview.org/thirteenth-amendment-optimism/" class="external text external">the original</a> on January 7, 2015.</cite> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20151117023919/http://columbialawreview.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/1733-1768.pdf" class="external text external" id="mwC18">Pdf.</a></li>
